#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "Account language"</h2>
You can select which language this software will display its output in
though if you are sharing content with other users, that content will
not be translated.
<p>This page will try to guess what language you are likely to use by
the context the page was invoked in, but if it can't figure out, it will
use the software developer's language (English).
